{"tid":480764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一面倒為台灣球后加油！香港羽球迷讓中國網友崩潰","createTime":"2017-11-26T12:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T04:30:15.000Z","uid":5195,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d788ea13c366d5f64491217f0b824596f7cbfdbf","tid":480764,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"世界球后戴資穎在香港超級賽出場大受歡迎，日前對中國球員陳雨菲的比賽中更是讓地主香港球迷「倒戈」，一面倒為台灣之光加油吶喊，不過這讓部份中國網友看的很不是滋味。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在中國媒體新浪新聞底下留言，表示當天的香港觀眾都在給戴資穎加油根本是「心理變態！」，該留言也引發許多網友的關注，有人認為看完那場比賽沒有覺得不正常，因為一般來說賽點、局點都會給球員加油，而且為頂級球星加油是人之常情，反嗆留言者才心理變態。"},{"pid":"c4288dd24ce6d3ca14368c92f741feb00ea2a7a6","tid":480764,"uid":42820,"like":65,"dislike":5,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"台灣人不是中國人嗎??"},{"pid":"771c8313a7c44ae80b0ea8d46cd29005e5544fc9","tid":480764,"uid":48419,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣人不是中國人嗎??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩牙都系中國人"},{"pid":"d0499ed1fa401c51eef775e73a49698373511f7f","tid":480764,"uid":22858,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支那出賽永遠支持對家</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b92332cdb687083dc0743fefad9e3f30732eb3","tid":480764,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:05:56.000Z","msg":"求片"},{"pid":"21cbe2ce9bd1972336cd9557e261dd8f85b33a4c","tid":480764,"uid":90634,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"班支那狗一邊講台灣係大陸<br />\n其實心入面一早承認台灣係獨立國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日中國台灣 醜唔醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5225257cf2dac54d0904d819a03a2065208a4e7c","tid":480764,"uid":36551,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"又話